  "tosSection2Para1": "You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service. If you are under 18, you represent that your parent or legal guardian has read and agreed to these AGB on your behalf.",
  "tosSection2Para2": "You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for Alle activities that occur under your account. Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.",
  "tosSection3Title": "Gesundheit Information — Not Medical Advice",
  "tosSection3Para1": "{appName} is a Gesundheit companion application intended for informational and organizational purposes only. The Service is NOT a medical device and does not provide medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment recommendations.",
  "tosSection3Para2": "The AI Triage feature provides general guidance based on the Symptome you report. It is not a substitute for professional medical judgment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare provider with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition. Never disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you read in this Service.",
  "tosSection3Para3": "In a medical eNotfall call your local Notfall number (e.g. 911, 112) immediately. Do not rely on the Service for Notfall response.",
  "tosSection4Title": "Use of the Service",
  "tosSection4Intro": "You agree NOT to:",
  "tosSection4Bullet1": "Use the Service for any unlawful purpose;",
  "tosSection4Bullet2": "Attempt to reverse-engineer, decompile, or disassemble the app;",
  "tosSection4Bullet3": "Upload content that is malicious, fraudulent, or violates intellectual property rights;",
  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Andere users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service to send unsolicited communications or spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Subscriptions & Payments",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EUnternehmen plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tAGB",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Abbrechen your subscription at any Zeit through your platform's account sEinstellungen",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will not apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Your Data",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Gesundheit data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Datenschutz Policy, which is incorporated into these AGB by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Exportieren your data at any Zeit via the in-app Exportieren feature, and you may permanently Löschen your account and Alle associated data via Einstellungen → Löschen Account.",
